section.wrapper#about
  section.wrapper_centered
    h2 About
    p
      | gendok is a node.js application used to render documents based on templates 
      | and content data provided by the user. For example, one could use gendok to 
      | generate customer bills which then can be retrieved as one or multiple PDF 
      | files. It places an emphasis on using existing web standards, so users can 
      | start using it right away, without having to learn any new languages or 
      | complicated APIs. It makes heavy use of HTML, CSS and well-known templating 
      | engines like Jade or Mustache. 
      br
      br
    p
      | gendok is intended to run as Software as a Service (SaaS) providing 
      | an extensive REST API as well as a graphical user interface (GUI).
